    "content": {
        "title": "Layout Top Properties",
        "body": "<ol>\n<li>From the <strong>Project</strong> explorer expand <strong>Mobile</strong> &gt; <strong>Forms</strong> &gt; <strong>frmFlex</strong> and select <strong>btnLayout</strong>.</li>\n<li>Navigate to the <strong>Properties</strong> panel on the top right of your canvas and select the <strong>Look</strong> tab.</li>\n<li>Under the <strong>Flex</strong> section, set the <strong>Top</strong> property to <strong>0 Dp</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Notice the button is now docked to the top of the screen on the canvas.</p>"
